      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## mdk - business of record (ADR 095)\nLive panels from the **real `movate` Postgres** (the authoritative store: `runs`, `workflow_runs`, cost). This is the Postgres half of the unified pane (ADR 095 D3); pair with the Prometheus metric dashboards for the full picture. Cost is extracted from `runs.metrics->>'cost_usd'`."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Workflow runs by status",
      "type": "piechart",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "postgres-movate"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "pieType": "donut",
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": [
            "value"
          ]
        },
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "postgres-movate"
          },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT status AS metric, count(*) AS value FROM workflow_runs GROUP BY status ORDER BY value DESC"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Workflow runs by runtime (native vs temporal)",
      "type": "piechart",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "postgres-movate"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "pieType": "donut",
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": [
            "value"
          ]
        },
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "postgres-movate"
          },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT coalesce(runtime,'native') AS metric, count(*) AS value FROM workflow_runs GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY value DESC"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Workflows seen (by name)",
      "type": "piechart",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "postgres-movate"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 16,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
